        "Idle",
        "hangup"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把主干画出来：Idle通过dial到Dialing，Dialing通过calling到Ringing，Ringing通过hangup回到Idle。那对方接听后呢？",
